0.12-alpha.description:
A small overhaul of the mod including changes to handle logic both in and out of game by adding a Terminal for missions.
Coded to work with the mod.io archipelago Archi_1.12a Update.

- Elimination missions now expect a single ammo buff
- More logic added to secondaries
- New Terminal Added to handle in game logic
0.12-alpha.title: 0.12 Alpha

0.13.2.description:
- Fixed many mismatch issues in 0.13 between regions and locations

**NOTE: If you generated a (multi)world with 0.13 you can still complete it, but it is recommended that you restart with 0.13.2 for the full experience**

Beta.description:
Moving into Beta we have a solid foundation for the mod.

The next goal will be to add more options to the yaml for configurations.

### Changes this Update

**NEW OPTIONS**
- You can now select one or all of the starting classes in your starting inventory (Defaults to gunner)

**NEW LOCATIONS**
- Machine Events (Haz 1-5)
- Warnings (Haz 1-5)
- Error Cubes (10 count)

**NEW ITEMS**
- Class specific buffs (Drills, Turrets, Shield Generator, Etc)
- The Bar (No beer until you get this check XD)
- Free drinks
- Gear Upgrade Tiers
- Overclocks (one check to be allowed to use them O.o)
- Mission Mutators (low gravity, blood sugar, etc)
- Classes (Engineer, Driller, Scout, Gunner) [You can optionally lock these :D]
Beta.title: 0.13 Beta
